The effects (both of them) need drastic improvement.  The parses are embarassing in underscoring the limitations of the piece.  And I agree with Reflectone...if you're going to have an effect on "fire" spells, then it should impact all of them...not just dd.  Most of us have moved our primary attack spell to Jenikor -- and the epic doesn't touch it.  What good is that?
<br />

<br />
Rakrak
<br />
70 Arch Magus
<br />
Aphelion
<br />
Lanys T'yvl</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
